reviews.review_text:
Fun times Pretty killer show overall.  The sound here is 2nd to none.  I was at these shows, and they were more laid back than the rest of the tour.  Felt like the music was a lot more inspired at the time than listening to it here.  Still pretty damn good.  
I like The Rigger.  Those guys were funny as hell.  They shot us with laser pointers at shows in the Spring of '90 while we were hunkering waiting for the shows to start and at the break.  Once we tuned in, it was hilarious to watch them mess with people in the crowd from their perches.  
Miss those daze y'all.  Glad we were there.
